*Success Critera:*


1. The AI Model - Using Google's Framework

    Stating My Goal:
    Predict a student's exam score. I will need to create a unidimensional regression model.
    Success: The model will predict a student's score with an accuracy of 3% (e.g. if the real one was 94, 97 or 91 is the highest loss allowed).

2. The UX

    The user will input data about their attendance, sleep, age, and the amount of time they spent studying. They will then click a button.
    The user will be redirected to a page where they can see their predicted score and next steps, e.g. catching up on material. They will see some helpful resources.
    The user will have the option to try again.

